  "name": "RPlog_A_New_Venture",
  "title": "A New Venture",
  "summary": "In the anti-gravity Free Flight Dance Dome of Capital City, the smuggler Piper -- introducing herself as Elysia -- catches the eye of a roguish young pilot at the bar who calls himself Captain Jerat, though she knows him as McBride. Over drinks they trade flirtatious, guarded banter: he claims to be a 'space-bum' captain of a standard freighter scouting heavy contracting rumors in the Slice, while she complains of being stuck and stagnant under the watchful Corporate Sector Authority. As the patrons dance overhead and the bubble-blowing acrobat Kian and the watchful newcomer Dagny look on, Piper angles for passage off-world and McBride offers to take her somewhere once his business concludes. When talk turns to the Authority's curious crackdown on Wookiees, Piper warns the walls have ears and proposes they continue aboard his ship; the two agree to meet again in two hours, and McBride departs to fetch a part.",
